text: Quo Vadis, Aida? ( Where are you going, Aida?) is a 2020 Bosnian Austrian Romanian Dutch German Polish French Norwegian Turkish war drama movie directed by Jasmila Žbanić and starring Jasna Đuričić, Izudin Bajrović, Boris Isaković, Johan Heldenbergh, Raymond Thiry, Boris Ler, Dino Bajrović.
